"(pressed)" => "(按下)"
"(released)" => "(松开)"
"(during)" => "(跟随)"
"(thread-down)" => "(独立线程按下)"
"(thread-up)" => "(独立线程松开)"
"(repeat)" => "(重复)"
"(sticky repeat)" => "(粘滞键重复)"
"(sticky hold)" => "(粘滞键按下)"
"(pressed & released)" => "(按下与松开)" #-- Added in 2.4 Beta 12 --
"(custom)" => "(自定义)" #-- Added in 2.17 Beta 9 --

#Section: Simulated Keystrokes dialog
"Simulated Keystrokes" => "模拟点击" #-- Updated in 2.4 Beta 15 --
"Enter the custom key(s)" => "请输入自定义按键"
"How to send the simulated key strokes:" => "如何键入这个模拟按键:"
"1 As mouse button is pressed" => "1 鼠标按键按下时键入"
"2 As mouse button is released" => "2 鼠标按键松开时键入"
"3 During (press on down, release on up)" => "3 按下期间保持状态 (跟随按键按下与松开)"
"4 In another thread as mouse button is pressed" => "4 在独立线程中鼠标按键按下时键入"
"5 In another thread as mouse button is released" => "5 在独立线程中鼠标按键松开时松开"
"6 Repeatedly while the button is down" => "6 按键按下时不断重复"
"7 Sticky (repeatedly until button is pressed again)" => "7 粘滞键 (重复键入，直到按键被再次按下)"
"8 Sticky (held down until button is pressed again)" => "8 粘滞键 (按下不放，直到按键被再次按下)"
"9 As mouse button is pressed & when released" => "9 鼠标按键按下与松开时均键入" #-- Added in 2.4 Beta 12 --
"Only send if profile's process is active" => "仅在配置文件指定的进程活动时发送键入操作"
"Block original mouse input" => "拦截原始鼠标输入" #-- Added in 2.7 Beta 5 --
"Block original mouse input only if active window matches profile" => "仅在活动窗口匹配当前配置时拦截原始鼠标输入" #-- Added in 2.20 Beta 4 --
"Randomise auto repeat delay by 10%" => "自动重复随机 (10%) 延时" #-- Added in 2.11 Beta 6 --
"Auto repeat delay" => "自动重复延迟"
"(milliseconds)" => "(毫秒)"
"0 = Windows default repeat delay && speed." => "0 = 系统的默认重复延迟与速度。"

# -- Added in 2.19 beta 3 --
"Click this button to add {} tags" => "点击此按钮添加 {} 标记"
"Hold this button and press a key to add that key's tag" => "按住这个按键并按下一个键以添加该键的标记"

# -- Added in 2.19 Beta 4
"Drop down button to select a tag from the menu" => "按下下拉按钮并从菜单中选择一个标记"

# -- Added in 2.19 Beta 8
"Right click to select a tag from the menu" => "右击从菜单中选择一个标记" #Windows XP Only (as it down not support dropdown split button)

