#Section: About Dialog
"XML support provided by XML++ from Michael at turboirc.com" => "XML 支持由 turboirc.com 网站的 Michael 制作的 XML++ 提供"
"XMBC is distributed freely (with no warranty or guarantee) for the use of anyone, anywhere. If you like XMBC and wish to show your appreciation please feel free to make a donation by clicking the PayPal button below." => "XMBC 为免费发布 (不需要授权，亦无担保) ，任何人可在任何地点使用。如果您喜欢 XMBC 并希望表达您的赞赏，您可以点击下方的 PayPal 按钮进行捐赠。"
