"An error occurred while running the update package" => "运行更新包时出错"

# -- Updated in 2.14 Beta 9
"Click here for more details." => "点击此处查阅更多信息。"

# -- Added in 2.10 Beta 12 --
"Downloading" => "正在下载"
"Launching the update installation..." => "正在开始安装更新..."
"Downloading update..." => "正在下载更新..." #Initial progress on download dialog
"Downloaded %d of %d bytes" => "已下载 %d / %d 字节" #Progress on download dialog

#Section: Button Chording
# -- Added in 2.14 Beta 1 --
"Button Chording" => "按键和弦"
"Default (No Chord)" => "默认 (无和弦)"
"Button chording allows you to make assign chorded actions that apply when one button is pressed, followed by a second button." => "按键和弦允许您分配“和弦”操作，即一个按键被按下后再按下第二个按键。"

# -- Added in 2.14 Beta 3 --
"&Block / Delay original button action until chord is established" => "阻止或延迟原始按键动作直至构成和弦"

# -- Added in 2.15 Beta 11 --
"&Unblock after" => "在指定时间之后解除阻止"
"Unblock when the mouse moves" => "在鼠标移动时解除阻止" #-- Added in 2.16 Beta 2 --

# -- Added in 2.14 Beta 8
"Change Log:" => "更新日志:"
"Unable to locate change log!" => "无法找到更新日志！"
"&Upgrade" => "升级[&U]" #Fixed in 2.16 Beta 14
"&Skip" => "跳过[&S]" #Fixed in 2.16 Beta 14

# -- Added in 2.17 Beta 4 and updated in 2.17 beta 5 --

#Section Button Held Time Dependent Actions
"Button Held Time Dependent Actions" => "按键保持时间相关动作"
"Define different actions based on how long you hold the mouse button down for when clicking." => "根据点击时按键保持时间的长短定义不同动作。"
"Normal Click" => "正常点击"
"Held for" => "保持时间"
"Held for time for action %d must be greater than that for action %d." => "动作 %d 的保持时间必须大于动作 %d。" #NOTE: The %d's are interpreted at runtime. Leave them there

# Added in 2.17 Beta 6
"&Abort and revert to the normal click action when the mouse moves." => "在鼠标移动时中止并恢复至正常的点击动作"
"NOTE: All but the last enable action above will not be performed until the button is released (once the hold time has been determined). The last action will be started once the minimum time period is reached." => "注意: 在被启用的所有动作中，除最后一个之外的所有动作都仅会在按键被释放 (且按键保持时间达标) 时执行，最后一个动作将在按键保持时间达到后立即执行。" #Removed in 2.18 Beta 7 (see below) 
"NOTE: All but the last enabled 'held for' action above will not be performed until the button is released (once the hold time has been determined). The last action will be started once the minimum time period is reached." => "注意: 在被启用的所有按键保持动作中，除最后一个之外的所有动作都仅会在按键被释放 (且按键保持时间达标) 时执行，最后一个动作将在按键保持时间达到后立即执行。" #Changed in 2.18 Beta 7

# Added in 2.18 Beta 7
"&Wait until the physical button is released before releasing the last timed action" => "最后一个动作也等到按键被释放时才执行"

# Added in 2.17 Beta 7
"Description (to show in button drop-down)" => "描述 (将在按键下拉菜单中展示)"

#Added in 2.17 beta 16
"Button Held" => "按键保持"

# Added in 2.20 Beta 3
"Abor&t and revert to the last held action when the mouse moves." => "在鼠标移动时中止并恢复至上一个按键保持动作。"

# Added in 2.20.1 / 2.21 Beta 1
"The selected file could not be imported." => "选定的文件无法被导入。"

#Added in 2.20.2
"Unable to check for updates! An unexpected error occurred." => "无法检查更新！发生意外错误。"
"Unable to check for updates! A DNS query error occurred." => "无法检查更新！DNS查询出错。"
